# {{WORKSPACE_NAME}} Devteam Workspace

This workspace is managed by devteam.

Daily entry:

```bash
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" workspace context --root "$PWD" --for human --text
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" track list --root "$PWD" --active-only --text
```

After selecting a track:

```bash
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" track context --root "$PWD" --set "<track>" --text
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" status --root "$PWD" --set "<track>"
```

Core concepts:

- Track: a named development/validation line.
- Worktree: local repo checkout used by a track.
- Run: auditable `.devteam/runs/<id>/` validation session.
- Evidence: recorded sync/test/publish/image/deploy results.
- Env profile: remote venv/server or local environment profile.
- Image profile: image build contract and gate.
- Deploy profile: pre-production deployment target and verification contract.

